## Install

X-Ways auto-loads X-Tensions from an `xtensions\` subfolder of the install. Drop
the per-tool folder in place:

```text
<X-Ways install>\
    ├── xwforensics64.exe        (or xwb64.exe for BYOD)
    └── xtensions\
        └── {{NAME}}\
            └── {{NAME}}.dll
```

## Run

X-Ways → **Tools → Run X-Tensions…** → select
`xtensions\{{NAME}}\{{NAME}}.dll`, choose your settings, and run.

